  <summary>Tinker with PDF files</summary>
  <description>
    <p>This desktop app reads and writes PDF documents. It was created for a small copy shop in Germany. Features of this application are:</p>
    <ul><li>Clone two or more PDF pages on one PDF page.</li>
    <li>Extract images from a PDF file</li>
    <li>Export PDF pages to JPG and PNG images</li>
    <li>Glue two PDF pages together to print them with a plotter</li>
    <li>Add, move and delete pages in a PDF document</li></ul>
  </description>
  
